         VERSION=1.3.0rc3
     SOURCE_HASH=sha512:0c1f461908e73b1611334e445ff94f13f5ee3fd1d63e842188460d6f6104ff8f77e927be4e15a4a90096ac71af7dcc7b1a67645c45dd98e82f017cee195a5ae3
